prompts.philosophy:
Express this week's collaboration philosophy with {{userName}} in JSON.
Format: { "quote": "3-4 line quote. Wrap the most important line in <span> tags.", "explanation": "2-3 line explanation" }
Be heartfelt and genuine. Output JSON only.

prompts.avatarDecor:
{{userName}} has the role "{{role}}". Analyze this user's domain and work, then pick fitting decorative emojis.
JSON format: { "decorEmojis": ["🛰️", "📡", "🌏", ...] }
Exactly 12. Return emoji array only. Output JSON only.

prompts.accentColor:
{{userName}} has the role "{{role}}". Recommend a fitting theme color for this user.
JSON format: { "accentColor": "#hexcode", "reason": "why this color" }
Output JSON only.
